message.body: Hey bub! Sorry we didn't make it to the dinner :( we'll have to have you and Danielle over sometime soon ok!! Miss ya
No worries ma. I totally understand. It'd be great to get out the city and see you guys. Lets make it happen. Let's keep in touch.
Ok sweet! Sunday's Mondays or Tuesday's are best!
Ok cool. I'm always off nights and weekends but Danielle's schedule changes all the time so I'll check in with her when she.gets her new schedules.
